name: Cyber Sea Creatures - Killun
description: Crustacean King Killun. One of the few remaining titan beasts living on Aquaz, a planet in the far reaches of the MLNDR universe. Bold, aggressive, and a bit of a temper with a love for getting right into the middle of the action. Abilities serrated titanium alloy pincers can cut through and break through just about anything. Dual mounted automatic chainlink plasma guns. Will allow an ally to mount on it's back to operate the weapons if they've developed a friendship, very loyal creature.
